== PageRank Task

Simplified algorithm:

----
PR(A) = (1-d) + d (PR(T1)/C(T1) + ... + PR(Tn)/C(Tn))
----

* +d+ - dampening factor
* +T+ - targets
* +C+ - count of dependencies

////
* Each target starts with a default PR.
* Iterate some number of times, or until reaching a stopping condition.
////


